Package com.opencloud.javax.sip

OpenCloud extensions to JAIN SIP.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ClientTransaction Experimental extension to the ClientTransaction interface.
ConnectionDownEvent Indicates that PersistentOutboundConnection has gone down.
ConnectionUpEvent Event emitted by a PersistentOutboundConnection activity when the connection comes up.
Endpoint Represents a local or remote SIP endpoint, a triple of host/port/transport.
LazyParsedMessage Messages in the OC SIP stack implement this interface.
OCMessage OC-proprietary extensions to Message.
PersistentOutboundConnection Activity representing a persistent outbound connection to a SIP host.
ServerTransaction Experimental extension to the ServerTransaction interface.
 

Exception Summary
LazyParsingException Thrown if the underlying stack supports lazy parsing, and a header failed to parse when the application requested the header value.
